OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after
OL,4,Cresidents found injured at care home
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after two woman
OL,8,Fwere injured at a care home in
OL,9,FWinchester.
OL,11,FPolice and ambulance crews were called
OL,12,Fto Westacre Nursing Home at Sleepers
OL,13,FHill at 9:03am on Monday (23 February).
OL,15,FTwo women - an 83-year-old and a
OL,16,Fwoman, 79, were both found with cuts
OL,17,Fto their upper body.
OL,19,FThey have been taken to hospital where
OL,20,Fthey remain in a stable condition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
