OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after
OL,4,Cresidents found injured at care home
OL,6,FPolice say enquiries are ongoing to
OL,7,Festablish how both women were injured,
OL,8,Fhowever officers believe they may have
OL,9,Fbeen assaulted.
OL,11,FA woman aged 49 has been arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of attempted murder and
OL,13,Fremains in custody.
OL,15,FNo other injuries have been reported.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
