OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after
OL,4,Cresidents found injured at care home
OL,6,FA Hampshire Police spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We would ask members of the public to
OL,8,Fcontact the home directly if they have
OL,9,Fany concerns about other residents,
OL,10,Fbut not attend for routine
OL,11,Fappointments while our investigation
OL,12,Fprogresses."
